'''阿爾斯特旗''' （{{lang-en|Flag of Ulster}}）是一面基於{{link-en|阿爾斯特紋章|Coat of arms of Ulster}}設計的旗幟，曾是代表[[阿爾斯特省|阿爾斯特省]]的旗幟。旗幟底色為金色，上有一紅色十字，中央是飾有紅手的白色盾牌。

== 歷史 ==
阿爾斯特旗出現在1264年，當時{{link-en|沃爾特·德伯格|Walter de Burgh, 1st Earl of Ulster}}成為{{link-en|阿爾斯特伯爵|Earldom of Ulster}}。他將德伯格家族的[[紋章|紋章]]（黃底紅十字）和伯爵領地的標誌[[阿爾斯特紅手|阿爾斯特紅手]]融合，形成了阿爾斯特紋章<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/life/features/does-northern-ireland-need-red-hand-sculpture-28535157.html |title=Does Northern Ireland need Red Hand sculpture? |work=Belfast Telegraph |date=2010-05-10 |access-date=2020-07-23 |archive-date=2021-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416135854/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/life/features/does-northern-ireland-need-red-hand-sculpture-28535157.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

據傳{{link-en|赫伯特·德伯格|Hubert de Burgh, 1st Earl of Kent}}在參加[[第三次十字軍東征|第三次十字軍東征]]時未有自己的紋章。他曾在一場戰役中使用金色盾牌。在戰場上，[[英格蘭王國|英格蘭]]國王[[理查一世|理查一世]]授予了德伯格紋章，並在金色盾牌上加上了紅色十字<ref>{{Cite book |last=Hernon |first=Ian |title=Fortress Britain: All the Invasions and Incursions since 1066 |url=https://archive.org/details/fortressbritaina0000hern |publisher=The History Press |year=2013 |isbn=978-0752497174 |page=[https://archive.org/details/fortressbritaina0000hern/page/n20 20]}}</ref>。

關於阿爾斯特紅手的起源則仍然是迷。一個流行的傳說稱在阿爾斯特王位的爭奪戰中，第一個到達阿爾斯特的人砍下他的手，並將其交給他的戰友<ref name="EriksenJenkins2007">{{Cite book |last1=Eriksen |first1=Thomas Hylland |title=Flag, Nation and Symbolism in Europe and America |url=https://archive.org/details/flagnationsymbol00jenk |last2=Jenkins |first2=Richard |publisher=Routledge |year=2007 |isbn=978-1-134-06696-4 |page=[https://archive.org/details/flagnationsymbol00jenk/page/n81 81] |author-link=Thomas Hylland Eriksen}}</ref>。愛爾蘭早期歷史的宗族戰爭存在爭議。馬格尼斯（Magennis）宗族和奧尼爾（O'Neill）都宣稱自己是{{link-en|烏拉德|Ulaid}}地區的國王。但1908年，當時的奧尼爾氏族統領承認其最初曾所屬於馬格尼斯氏族<ref name="ONeill180">O'Neill, The (1908). The Heraldic Emblem of Ireland. Ulster Journal of Archaeology, Second Series, Vol. 14, No. 4 (Nov.), pp. 178–180. Ulster Archaeological Society.</ref>。

關於旗幟的手應使用左手還是右手經常有爭議。雖然在旗幟上通常使用右手，但亦有部分組織使用左手<ref name="nl">{{Cite web |date=2016-06-03 |title=Loyalists get it right in left red hand debate |url=https://www.newsletter.co.uk/news/loyalists-get-it-right-left-red-hand-debate-1233632 |access-date=2020-05-15 |publisher=News Letter |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412124627/https://www.newsletter.co.uk/news/loyalists-get-it-right-left-red-hand-debate-1233632 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一些阿爾斯特省的郡亦在它們的紋章使用紅手，如[[安特里姆郡|安特里姆郡]]、[[弗馬納郡|弗馬納郡]]、[[倫敦德里郡|倫敦德里郡]]和[[蒂龍郡|蒂龍郡]]<ref name="coa">{{Cite news |title=All 32 Irish county coat of arms and where they come from |publisher=Irish Post |url=https://www.irishpost.com/news/all-32-irish-county-coat-of-arms-and-where-they-come-from-115697 |access-date=2020-05-15 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412204329/https://www.irishpost.com/news/all-32-irish-county-coat-of-arms-and-where-they-come-from-115697 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[勞斯郡|勞斯郡]]亦在文章中使用手的圖案，但其顏色是肌膚顏色，象徵上帝之手，而非阿爾斯特紅手<ref name=coa />。

== 顏色 ==
阿爾斯特旗使用金色<ref>{{Cite web |title=Pantone 123 C |url=https://www.pantone.com/color-finder/123-C |website=[[Pantone|Pantone]] |accessdate=2021-04-12 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412124626/https://www.pantone.com/color-finder/123-C |dead-url=no }}</ref>、紅色<ref>{{Cite web |title=Pantone 485 C |url=https://www.pantone.com/color-finder/485-C |website=[[Pantone|Pantone]] |accessdate=2021-04-12 |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417164708/https://www.pantone.com/color-finder/485-C |dead-url=no }}</ref> 和白色三種顏色。英國{{link-en|旗幟協會|Flag Institute}}和愛爾蘭旗幟學協會就阿爾斯特旗的用色有協議<ref>{{Cite web |last=Bartram |first=Graham |author-link=Graham Bartram |title=Ulster |url=https://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/flags/ulster |website=Flag Institute |accessdate=2021-04-12 |archive-date=2020-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217094605/http://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/flags/ulster |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

