== 20世紀 ==
[[File:Flag_of_Northern_Ireland_(1953–1972).svg|thumb]]]]
在20世紀[[愛爾蘭分治|愛爾蘭分治]]之後，阿爾斯特旗成為[[紅手旗|紅手旗]]的設計基礎。紅手旗是北愛爾蘭的代表旗幟，底色改為白色；中央的盾牌改為六角星，象徵構成北愛爾蘭的六個郡；六角星上方是王國，象徵對[[英國|英國]]的忠誠<ref>{{Cite web |last=Smith |first=Whitney |title=Flag of Northern Ireland |url=https://www.britannica.com/topic/flag-of-Northern-Ireland |access-date=2020-05-15 |publisher=Britannica |archive-date=2020-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010074717/https://www.britannica.com/topic/flag-of-Northern-Ireland |dead-url=no }}</ref>。紅手旗有時被稱為「六郡旗」，而阿爾斯特旗有時被稱為「九郡旗」<ref name="UlsterFlags">{{Cite web |title=Physical Memorials of The Troubles in Belfast by Elisabetta Viggiani - Introduction |url=https://cain.ulster.ac.uk/viggiani/introduction.htm |access-date=2020-05-15 |publisher=Ulster University |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412124627/https://cain.ulster.ac.uk/viggiani/introduction.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。「紅手旗」有時也可代指阿爾斯特旗<ref name="UlsterFlags" /><ref>{{Cite news |last=Murtagh |first=Peter |date=2017-07-13 |title=Eleventh night: 'It's community, it's family and it's culture' |publisher=Irish Times |url=https://www.irishtimes.com/news/ireland/irish-news/eleventh-night-it-s-community-it-s-family-and-it-s-culture-1.3152802 |access-date=2020-05-15 |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204212135/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/ireland/irish-news/eleventh-night-it-s-community-it-s-family-and-it-s-culture-1.3152802 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Biermann |first=Christoph |date=2017-10-05 |title=Why not! |url=https://11freunde.de/artikel/why-not/528791 |access-date=2020-05-26 |publisher=11 Freunde |language=de |archive-date=2020-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805135906/https://11freunde.de/artikel/why-not/528791 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=The anti-Brexit protester flying Ulster flag and tricolour at Westminster |publisher=Belfast Telegraph |url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/brexit/the-anti-brexit-protester-flying-ulster-flag-and-tricolour-at-westminster-37861986.html |access-date=2020-05-26 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412124625/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/brexit/the-anti-brexit-protester-flying-ulster-flag-and-tricolour-at-westminster-37861986.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年，按{{link-en|蘇格蘭警察|Police Scotland}}的[[信息自由|信息自由]]要求，在蘇格蘭挑釁性展示阿爾斯特旗可能被視為犯罪行為，最高可處以五年徒刑<ref>{{Cite news |last=Swinson |first=Peter |title=Revealed: the police list of flags that could be criminal offence to fly in Scotland |publisher=Herald Scotland |url=https://www.heraldscotland.com/news/16897189.revealed-the-police-list-of-flags-that-could-be-criminal-offence-to-fly-in-scotland/ |access-date=2020-05-26 |archive-date=2020-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200514034018/https://www.heraldscotland.com/news/16897189.revealed-the-police-list-of-flags-that-could-be-criminal-offence-to-fly-in-scotland/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 體育用途 ==
阿爾斯特旗用於體育賽事。同時代表北愛爾蘭和愛爾蘭共和國的[[愛爾蘭國家橄欖球隊|愛爾蘭國家橄欖球隊]]在其主場同時使用[[愛爾蘭國旗|愛爾蘭國旗]]和阿爾斯特旗<ref>{{Cite journal |date=2018-03-07 |title=Poll: In a united Ireland, would it be appropriate to change the Irish national flag? |url=https://www.thejournal.ie/your-say-irish-flag-3889347-Mar2018/ |publisher=The Journal |access-date=2020-05-15 |journal= |archive-date=2021-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415050801/https://www.thejournal.ie/your-say-irish-flag-3889347-Mar2018/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{link-en|愛爾蘭橄欖球協會|Irish Rugby Football Union}}的中立旗幟包括了愛爾蘭四省旗，其中包括阿爾斯特旗<ref>{{Cite web |date=2015-09-15 |title=Buy The Flag And Fly The Flag |url=https://www.irishrugby.ie/2015/09/15/buy-the-flag-and-fly-the-flag/ |access-date=2020-05-15 |publisher=Irish Rugby Football Union |archive-date=2021-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424141021/https://www.irishrugby.ie/2015/09/15/buy-the-flag-and-fly-the-flag/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[世界盃橄欖球賽|世界盃橄欖球賽]]時，兩面旗幟均有使用<ref>{{Cite news |last=Suzanne McGonagle |date=2019-09-23 |title=Ireland begin World Cup campaign with convincing win against Scotland in Japan |publisher=The Irish News |url=http://www.irishnews.com/paywall/tsb/irishnews/irishnews/irishnews//sport/2019/09/23/news/ireland-begin-world-cup-campaign-with-convincing-win-against-scotland-in-japan-1719319/content.html |access-date=2020-05-15 |archive-date=2021-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424141044/https://www.irishnews.com/paywall/tsb/irishnews/irishnews/irishnews//sport/2019/09/23/news/ireland-begin-world-cup-campaign-with-convincing-win-against-scotland-in-japan-1719319/content.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{link-en|阿爾斯特橄欖球|Ulster Rugby}}的部分球迷使用阿爾斯特旗，部分則使用紅手旗<ref>{{Cite news |title=Season Ticket, 2009/10, Party Like It's 1999 |publisher=BBC |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00j4c7l |access-date=2020-05-15 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412124625/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00j4c7l |dead-url