==作為其他旗幟的一部分==
作為四省旗（Four Provinces Flag）的一部分，阿爾斯特旗經常和[[倫斯特省|倫斯特省]]、[[芒斯特省|芒斯特省]]、[[康諾特省|康諾特省]]的旗幟一同出現，作為代表{{link-en|全愛爾蘭|All-Ireland}}的運動隊旗幟使用<ref name="hs">{{Cite news |title=Revealed: the police list of flags that could be criminal offence to fly in Scotland |publisher=Herald Scotland |url=https://www.heraldscotland.com/news/16897189.revealed-the-police-list-of-flags-that-could-be-criminal-offence-to-fly-in-scotland/ |access-date=2020-05-15 |archive-date=2020-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200514034018/https://www.heraldscotland.com/news/16897189.revealed-the-police-list-of-flags-that-could-be-criminal-offence-to-fly-in-scotland/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，如{{link-en|愛爾蘭男子草地曲棍球代表隊|Ireland men's national field hockey team}}的旗幟<ref name=hs />。
